

{"id":6051,"date":"2024-03-05T10:20:12","date_gmt":"2024-03-05T03:20:12","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/?p=6051"},"modified":"2024-03-11T17:19:18","modified_gmt":"2024-03-11T10:19:18","slug":"6-bai-tap-gian-co-tot-nhat-cho-co-dui-san-chac","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/6-bai-tap-gian-co-tot-nhat-cho-co-dui-san-chac\/","title":{"rendered":"6 b\u00e0i t\u1eadp gi\u00e3n c\u01a1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i s\u0103n ch\u1eafc"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u0103ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i sau l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n do c\u1ea3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y ra c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u0103ng v\u00e0 \u0111au. D\u00f9 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng, \u00edt v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n, ho\u1eb7c \u1edf m\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i sau c\u0103ng, b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u00e0 mang l\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng tin h\u1eefu \u00edch v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn c\u0103ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i sau?<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u0103ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i sau, nh\u01b0ng th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 n\u00e0y thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1: ng\u1ed3i l\u00e2u v\u00e0 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Ng\u1ed3i l\u00e2u<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ng\u1ed3i l\u00e2u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u00f9i sau b\u1ecb c\u0103ng. Khi ch\u00fang ta ng\u1ed3i xu\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i cong, c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i sau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef \u1edf t\u01b0 th\u1ebf r\u00fat ng\u1eafn. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ng\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng gi\u1edd m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f9i sau c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb gi\u1eef \u1edf tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i r\u00fat ng\u1eafn, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y c\u0103ng c\u1ee9ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed nghi\u00eang x\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1eadu v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda sau, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111au l\u01b0ng d\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u01b0 th\u1ebf trong su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y, bao g\u1ed3m chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb ng\u1ed3i sang \u0111\u1ee9ng, th\u00eam c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c gi\u00e3n c\u01a1 v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho \u0111\u00f9i sau v\u00e0 c\u01a1 m\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u0103ng c\u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>T\u01b0 th\u1ebf x\u1ea5u<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u01b0 th\u1ebf x\u1ea5u c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f9i sau v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u01a1 kh\u00e1c. X\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1eadu nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c, m\u1ed9t t\u01b0 th\u1ebf ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn khi\u1ebfn x\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1eadu b\u1ecb xoay v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 g\u1ea5p h\u00f4ng ng\u1eafn l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f9i sau d\u00e0i ra, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00f9i sau b\u1ecb c\u0103ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c v\u00e0 y\u1ebfu.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn x\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1eadu nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u1ed3i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong ng\u00e0y, g\u00e2y ra c\u00e1c c\u01a1 g\u1ea5p h\u00f4ng c\u0103ng k\u00e9o x\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1eadu c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, k\u00e9o d\u00e0i c\u01a1 g\u1ea5p h\u00f4ng v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho \u0111\u00f9i sau v\u00e0 c\u01a1 m\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n gi\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u0103ng c\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00f9i sau.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1eb7c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 nhanh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111au nh\u1ee9c c\u01a1 kh\u1edfi ph\u00e1t mu\u1ed9n, c\u0103ng c\u01a1 v\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. C\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i sau c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng cho nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i b\u00e0i t\u1eadp kh\u00e1c nhau, ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 ch\u1ea1y, \u0111\u1ea1p xe, n\u00e2ng t\u1ea1 v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao kh\u00e1c, v\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng l\u1eadp k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>C\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c c\u0103ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i sau<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi\u1ec7c kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i sau b\u1ecb c\u0103ng th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c du\u1ed7i c\u01a1. Vi\u1ec7c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c du\u1ed7i cho c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i sau, b\u1eafp ch\u00e2n, c\u01a1 m\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u01a1 g\u1eadp h\u00f4ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, gi\u1ea3m th\u1eddi gian ng\u1ed3i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 t\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i sau c\u0103ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b>6 b\u00e0i t\u1eadp gi\u00e3n c\u01a1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111\u00f9i sau s\u0103n ch\u1eafc<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c gi\u00e3n c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u00f9i sau b\u1ecb c\u0103ng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee9ng. B\u1ea1n n\u00ean t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp gi\u00e3n c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 t\u0129nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 \u0111\u1ebfn 3 l\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i gi\u00e3n c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i c\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y!<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp gi\u00e3n c\u01a1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111\u00f9i sau s\u0103n ch\u1eafc l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Hamstring scoops<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c k\u00e9o d\u00e3n n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 trong ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ee9ng hai ch\u00e2n r\u1ed9ng b\u1eb1ng h\u00f4ng<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Du\u1ed7i m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n ra ngo\u00e0i, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i h\u01a1i cong<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">U\u1ed1n cong h\u00f4ng, \u0111\u01b0a tay v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ch\u00e2n r\u1ed3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u1ea5t l\u00ean tr\u1ea7n nh\u00e0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf ch\u00e2n kia<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Standing knee hug<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c gi\u00e3n c\u01a1 n\u00e0y nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f9i sau, c\u01a1 m\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, khi\u1ebfn n\u00f3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i t\u1eadp to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o th\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ee9ng r\u1ed9ng b\u1eb1ng h\u00f4ng v\u00e0 t\u1eeb t\u1eeb nh\u1ea5c m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n l\u00ean tr\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi n\u1eafm v\u00e0 \u00f4m \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ng\u1ef1c<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gi\u1eef cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i khi du\u1ed7i ch\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ch\u00e2n xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e0n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai b\u00ean 3-4 l\u1ea7n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Seated hamstring stretch<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c gi\u00e3n c\u01a1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, t\u0129nh n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp gi\u00e3n c\u01a1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t d\u00e0nh cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i sau s\u0103n ch\u1eafc sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean s\u00e0n v\u1edbi hai ch\u00e2n du\u1ed7i th\u1eb3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u1eb3ng, xoay h\u00f4ng v\u00e0 u\u1ed1n cong v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb th\u1eaft l\u01b0ng xa nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f9i sau c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 h\u00e3y \u0111\u01b0a m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00ean \u0111\u00f9i trong v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung k\u00e9o c\u0103ng t\u1eebng \u0111\u00f9i sau m\u1ed9t l\u00fac<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gi\u1eef c\u0103ng trong 15-20 gi\u00e2y<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Lying hamstring stretch<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1eb1m ng\u1eeda v\u1edbi b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e0n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u00e2ng ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean, gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u00e0ng th\u1eb3ng c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u00f3n ch\u00e2n l\u00ean tr\u1ea7n nh\u00e0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gi\u1eef ph\u00eda sau \u0111\u00f9i ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng k\u00e9o ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ng\u1ef1c<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gi\u1eef c\u0103ng trong 10 \u2013 30 gi\u00e2y r\u1ed3i l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf ph\u00eda b\u00ean kia<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Standing hamstring stretch<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1eb3ng l\u01b0ng v\u00e0 nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t, h\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u00f3n ch\u00e2n l\u00ean tr\u1ea7n nh\u00e0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cong \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 xoay h\u00f4ng, nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 c\u0103ng \u1edf \u0111\u00f9i sau b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gi\u1eef l\u01b0ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh khom l\u01b0ng &#8211; d\u00f9ng tay l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00fang l\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i tr\u00e1i \u0111ang cong c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gi\u1eef t\u01b0 th\u1ebf k\u00e9o gi\u00e3n n\u00e0y trong 10 \u2013 30 gi\u00e2y r\u1ed3i l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Standing forward fold hamstring stretch<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y trong c\u00e1c l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc yoga, \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c du\u1ed7i \u0111\u00f9i sau khi \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u01a1 \u1edf chu\u1ed7i sau c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i c\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i m\u1ec1m<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ea3n l\u1ec1 \u1edf h\u00f4ng v\u00e0 g\u1eadp xu\u1ed1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi, gi\u1eef th\u1eb3ng ch\u00e2n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9 linh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o ng\u00f3n ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u2013 n\u1ebfu r\u01a1i v\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y, h\u00e3y \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng xa nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 gi\u1eef trong 20 \u2013 30 gi\u00e2y<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\">C\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i s\u0103n ch\u1eafc<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 gi\u00e3n c\u01a1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m \u0111au do \u0111\u00f9i sau b\u1ecb c\u0103ng nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u0103n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee9ng th\u00eam. T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i sau, c\u01a1 m\u00f4ng, c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, b\u1eafp ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u01a1 g\u1eadp h\u00f4ng s\u1ebd th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 b\u1eafp \u1edf ph\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, gi\u00fap ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u0103ng c\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee9ng t\u0103ng l\u00ean trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m d\u1ea7n theo th\u1eddi gian.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The New Gym khuy\u00ean b\u1ea1n n\u00ean t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1ed7i nh\u00f3m c\u01a1 2-3 l\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c b\u1ec1n. Squat, deadlifts v\u00e0 hip pushs \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o c\u00e1c c\u01a1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t \u0111\u00f9i sau, v\u00ec v\u1eady h\u00e3y th\u1eed th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y v\u00e0o th\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i t\u1eadp \u0111\u00f9i sau tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0:<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Romanian deadlifts<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Good mornings<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Prone hamstring curl<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Swiss ball hamstring curl<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kettlebell swings<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nordic curls<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Inchworms<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ng\u1ed3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft th\u1eddi gian trong ng\u00e0y t\u1ea1i n\u01a1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mu\u1ed1n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n b\u00e0i t\u1eadp k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t c\u01a1 m\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 b\u00e0i t\u1eadp ch\u00e2n n\u00e0o v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c gi\u00e3n c\u01a1 \u1edf tr\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u0103n kho\u0103n ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1eadp th\u1ebf n\u00e0o l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang ch\u01b0a? \u0110\u1eebng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i li\u00ean h\u1ec7 c\u00e1c\u00a0<em><a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/5-ly-do-nen-tap-luyen-cung-huan-luyen-vien-ca-nhan\/\">hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n<\/a><\/em>\u00a0c\u1ee7a\u00a0\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/thenewgymvietnam\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>The New Gym<\/strong><\/a>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The New Gym &#8211; Gym cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b